title: Crystal CPUID Portable [h33t][Give&Get]
description:
Intel/AMD CPUs. Freeware Application to set CPU Multiplyer factor and voltage:

In "Multiplyer Management Setting" you can set multiple overcklock and underclock settings whitch are than managed dynamically according to your system load... Maximum performance and cool Temperatures

Don&#039;t forget to start Funktion > Multiplyer Management (Or Press F3)
Developer Description:

   * Multiplier Management
   * Support AMD64/EM64T
   * Intel SpeedStep Control
   * AMD K6/K7/K8/GeodeLX Multiplier/Voltage Control
   * VIA CyrixIII/C3 Multiplier Control
   * MSR Editor/MSR Walker
   * Clock, Cache, System Clock, Multiplier
   * Feature Flags
   * CPUID
   * Process Rule
   * Code Name
   * Multi Processor
   * PCI Device List
   * Chipset/VGA information
   * BIOS Information

Hope you like it - It&#039;s good for your hardware and contributes to to safe energy
